    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1. The CFD model of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump is deemed sufficiently credible to support identification of worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for a Class II CPB device. Decision: Accepted.",
